{"tid":1940604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：美國很快將恢復經濟活動","createTime":"2020-03-24T01:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T03:58:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1b1b642786fc725d2e236032751efe7ff81135","tid":1940604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:21:28.000Z","msg":"下? 唔係嘛? &nbsp;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTrump而家應專注抗疫, 對中共報仇. &nbsp;遲D先再諗恢復經濟活動.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516425-20200324.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516425-20200324.htm&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1nhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=17636303\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516425-20200324.htm&h=5eadaf68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516425-20200324.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普：美國很快將恢復經濟活動<br />\n2020-03-24 HKT 09:00<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，正考慮並研究如何重新開放美國經濟。<br />\n<br />\n新型肺炎疫情在美國未見緩和跡象，特朗普在上星期呼籲民眾避免不必要的出行，部分州份已經停止經濟活動。<strong>特朗普在白宮的記者會上表示，美國很快將會「再次營業」，艾奧瓦、愛達荷等部分感染率相對較低的州份可能率先恢復經濟活動，華府不會考慮新的旅遊禁令，強調不會令疫情拖累經濟變成長期的經濟問題。<br />\n</strong><br />\n特朗普又感謝聯儲局擴大買債規模，他致電主席鮑威爾讚揚對方「做得好」。"},{"pid":"c22044a004e13a2ab8a9e41dcd0c5ec1bcaeb155","tid":1940604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd93662e2e084131356e5f3a77f3489689e7bd7","tid":1940604,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"忍 14 日，封關！"},{"pid":"d311610e4b5c2ad20d4302a50bc7e19f971b8365","tid":1940604,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd93662e2e084131356e5f3a77f3489689e7bd7","tid":1940604,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime